Lim-Plugin-DNS - DNS Manager plugin for Lim

ABOUT

This plugin manage generic DNS related information like zone files via Lim. It
does not manage DNS software specific information.

For available RPC calls and CLI commands please see:

	perldoc Lim::Plugin::DNS

LIMITATIONS

Zone file editing with regards to options and RRs are currently some what
limited.

    - All options are placed at the top
    - Order of options might change when modifying zone file
    - Order of RRs might change when modifying zone file

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Lim::Plugin::DNS

You can also look for information at:

    Issue tracker (report bugs here)
        http://github.com/jelu/lim-plugin-dns/issues

    GIT repository
        http://github.com/jelu/lim-plugin-dns


